// [v0.9.63] Personal resource defaults — seeded onto every character (protagonist and
// NPCs alike) so Stakes can target anyone with identical code. Direction convention:
// higher index = better. Health runs Dead(0) -> Healthy(last); a cost subtracts toward
// Dead, a heal adds toward Healthy. Pools clamp to min/max; tracks to 0..states-1.
